title: someone is on my account right now!
body:
Hello!

I saw a bunch of new friends and that i was in game! i tried changing my account pass. but i didnt kick the person off. What can i do to kick that person of my account? ty!

replies.body: Just login and it overrides it????
File a support ticket to Riot, they'll help you out
